headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Johnson & Johnson (JNJ) After Its Strong 1 Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Johnson & Johnson is still fairly priced after its recent run, this article will help you weigh what you are paying against what you are getting. The stock last closed at US$248.43, with reported returns of 2.4% over 7 days, 9.1% over 30 days, 19.8% year to date, 54.7% over 1 year and 83.3% over 5 years.
